  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">significant</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Phase Beam</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potential improvements include: <span class=\"name name-stellar\">damage output</span>, and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">overheat tolerance</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船相位光束</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害输出</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">耐热性</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船相位光束</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">显著</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>通过显著地提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">伤害</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">耐热性</span>来提升战斗效率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船相位光束</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">重大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能強化的項目包括：<span class=\"name name-stellar\">傷害輸出</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">過熱的承受能力</span>。"
